field. 
</P>
<P>
	Jeannie Longo-Ciprelli finished with the main field nine seconds  
out to retain the race leader's blue jersey for the seventh 
straight day. She leads by 71 seconds over runnerup Linda Jackson 
of Canada. 
  	   	
