industrial average is down 13.29 to 10,771.66. NYSE advancers lead 
decliners 1,256-1,107. Most active on the NYSE today is Compaq 
Computer, which issued a warning this morning that its earnings 
would fall short of expectations. Compaq is down 13/16 to 21 7/16. 
The Nasdaq Composite Index is up 13.06 to 2,530.89. 

