and the economy beginning at 10 a.m. EDT. 
</P>
<P>
	And investors are hoping they'll hear answers to questions about  
what the Fed plans to do with interest rates. 
</P>
<P>
	The Fed's next rate meeting takes place on the 29th and 30th of  
the month. 
  	   	
