<HEADLINE> House Roll Call on 10 Commandments </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	The 248-180 roll call Wednesday by which the House approved a  
measure allowing the Ten Commandments to be posted in schools and 
other government buildings. 
</P>
<P>
	A ``yes'' vote is a vote to approve the measure.  
</P>
<P>
